string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1_Ino_2_idle_s
string.body: Hey! Please listen to what I've got to say.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1_Ino_3_idle_s
string.body: We have a big problem! Krall are plotting, plotting something.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_015_Die_S
string.body: Grrrk, you know how to play.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_016_Batk_S
string.body: Kraark, you are not leaving just like that.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_030_Die_S
string.body: Please avenge my death, my lord Saendukal...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_035_Batk_S
string.body: Today... shall be the day... you die...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_038_Katk_S
string.body: Leave... if you don't want to die...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_040_Die_S
string.body: I'd rather have an eternal rest...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_041_Batk_B
string.body: You will regret... having come here, [%userclass]...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_052_Katk_S
string.body: Kraark, I'll show you the power of magic!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_053_Die_S
string.body: Grrrk, I will never forgive you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_060_Batk_S
string.body: Kraark, it's been a while since I last tasted blood!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_065_Die_S
string.body: Grrrk, you are not bad at all...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_066_Die_S
string.body: Please avenge my death, my lord Saendukal...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_071_Katk_S
string.body: Kraark, I'll give you a hot lesson!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_076_Batk_S
string.body: Kraark, how dare you come here!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_078_Katk_S
string.body: You not so bad. Worthy opponent!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_084_Katk_S
string.body: Here, just take two more hits!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_085_Katk_S
string.body: Here, just take one more hit!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_095_Batk_S
string.body: You don't seem to be afraid of me.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_097_Die_S
string.body: It hurts, I don't want to die.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_098_Idle_S
string.body: I worked too long and I'm tired.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_099_Idle_S
string.body: I can't work, I'm too hungry.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_100_Batk_S
string.body: I'll hit you just a little.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_102_Atk_S
string.body: Just go down already, blast it...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_103_Flee_S
string.body: Spare me! I only did what I was told to do.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_104_Die_S
string.body: There are still so many things to do...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_105_Die_S
string.body: So, this is how Kobold dies...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_106_Idle_S
string.body: I work too much. It's hard.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_107_Idle_S
string.body: And they don't even give us enough food to live on! What a life, nyerk.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_113_Die_S
string.body: I want to be born as a Krall in next life...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_GOBLIN_002
string.body: The meal-time bell has rung! Time to eat!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_GOBLIN_003
string.body: It's the meal-time bell! Time to eat!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_GOBLIN_005
string.body: I'm very hungry! I'm going to eat and eat a lot.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_119_Batk_S
string.body: Kraark, what an absurd pup! Daring to attack me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_120_Katk_S
string.body: I shall soak this place with your blood!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_123_Katk_S
string.body: I'll show you the true horror!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_124_Die_S
string.body: How, how did I... To, to a mere Elyos...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_125_Die_S
string.body: I will never forget this shame...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_127_Idle_S
string.body: I will brief you on your mission.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_128_Idle_S
string.body: The time has come to reveal the hidden power of the Elyos.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_129_Atk_S
string.body: [%userclass], someone is waiting for you at the Outer Dock!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_130_Atk_S
string.body: Hey, [%userclass], go to the Outer Dock!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_131_Atk_S
string.body: Go and talk to Bella in the Outer Dock.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_132_Atk_S
string.body: Hey you [%userclass], what are you dallying about?

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_133_Atk_S
string.body: Leave this place to me and just go!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_134_Atk_S
string.body: Are you [%username]? Let us leave quickly!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_137_Atk_S
string.body: Are you all right over there?

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_138_Eatk_S
string.body: So, there is one less after this...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_139_Batk_S
string.body: There is not even a moment to rest, eh...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_141_Atk_S
string.body: I won't let you get away from me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_142_Eatk_S
string.body: You will not set a single foot in here as long as I'm around!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_144_Atk_S
string.body: Get out of here right now!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_150_Eatk_S
string.body: Just when is the reinforcement going to come...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_153_Idle_S
string.body: The shaman is looking for you [%usergender], so go quickly.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_154_Idle_S
string.body: The shaman is waiting for you below the ruins to the northwest from here.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_155_Idle_S
string.body: I sense something ominous in the west.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_156_Idle_S
string.body: What will be the fate of Elysea...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_160_Idle_S
string.body: Now even they are... Just what are they intending to do?

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_161_Idle_S
string.body: Lately, I've been seeing a number of shady characters.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_162_Idle_S
string.body: I hear there are some curious creatures in the Krall encampment.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_164_Idle_S
string.body: Are you here to receive supplies?

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_166_Idle_S
string.body: Hold this place with your life!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_167_Batk_S
string.body: Confound it, they are here again!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_170_Eatk_S
string.body: I'm so sick and tired of these battles!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_171_Batk_S
string.body: Hahaha! You dare to attack me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_FIELDOBJECT_001
string.body: It cannot be used right now.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_SHANDURA_001
string.body: You'll see how fearsome this sword is!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_181_Idle_S
string.body: Are you [%username]? I have been waiting for you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_182_Idle_S
string.body: Are you the [%userclass] who volunteered for the advance party?

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_183
string.body: You cowards, ganging up like this on just one foe!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_184_Atk_S
string.body: It's all right! We can win!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_185_Atk_S
string.body: Keep it up for just a little longer.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_186_Atk_S
string.body: You will not escape from here!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_188_Atk_S
string.body: You aren't so bad for a Krall!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_189_Atk_S
string.body: You are no match for me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_191_Atk_S
string.body: Ugh, you are not bad at all...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_192_Idle_S
string.body: Oh no, the shaman's prophecy is really going to...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_199_Atk_S
string.body: You aren't so bad, are you? But still there is no way you will defeat me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_200_Idle_S
string.body: There must be something important to take care of, [%usergender], for you to have come all the way here.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_201_Idle_S
string.body: There are many Krall about, so be careful around here!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_202_Idle_S
string.body: When the bell rings we eat.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_203_Idle_S
string.body: I want to eat. Ring the bell.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_205_Idle_S
string.body: I'm hungry. I hope the bell rings soon.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_GOBLIN_HELP_002
string.body: Master gave an order! Kobold attack!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_WARNING_BELL_002
string.body: It is the alarm! Kraark, what is happening?

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_WARNING_BELL_003
string.body: Kraark, good. It's been a while since I had a workout!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_206_Katk_S
string.body: Rise again, the spirit of Darkness!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_207_Katk_S
string.body: Answer my call, the spirit of the dead!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_208_Katk_S
string.body: O walking deads, fight for Lord Saendukal!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_MUSHROOM_POLYMORPH_001
string.body: You feel a strange sensation. You have turned into a mushroom.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_GOBLIN_MANAGER_001
string.body: I do not run! I fight to the end!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1A_LUSIS_1_Waypoint
string.body: The Kobolds are rather quiet today.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1A_Naia_1_WayPoint
string.body: The porgus is quite fat, looks like Cannon has been feeding it well.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_NPC_Ulaguru_2_idle_s
string.body: Kraark, I'm hungry. Marmeia! When are you going to feed me?

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_NPC_Ulaguru_3_idle_s
string.body: Kraark, Krall are much stronger than Daevas!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_NPC_Ulaguru_4_idle_s
string.body: Kraark, you better be prepared! Soon my brothers will come to rescue me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_003_Idle_S
string.body: Wow! It is the Protector of Sanctum, [%username]!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_004_Idle_S
string.body: Now that [%username] is here, the tide of the battle should turn in our favor.

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_013_Atk_S
string.body: We will not let you wretches to take the Abyss!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_015_Atk_S
string.body: So, what do you think? The power of Pandaemonium, that is!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_018_Atk_S
string.body: Do you sense the power of Archon?

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_022_Idle_S
string.body: [%username], please show those wretches the might of Sanctum!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_024_Batk_S
string.body: I smell an Elyos. There is an intruder!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_025_Batk_S
string.body: It is the punishment of Lord Orissan!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_030_Batk_S
string.body: Who the hell is it? Who dares to disturb my slumber!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_033_Die_S
string.body: What a shameful way to die, defeated by a Guardian!

string.name: STR_CHAT_postman_03_Idle_B
string.body: Time is silver my friend, akakak!

string.name: STR_CHAT_postman_04_Idle_B
string.body: There is no mail for you, nyerk.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Farmer_002_Atk_B
string.body: I spent so much time and effort to grow these crops!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Guard_001_Atk_S
string.body: There is just no end to them and they keep coming!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Guard_002_Atk_S
string.body: These accursed wretches do not even tire!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Shugo_001_Idle_S
string.body: We have some nice stuff! Come and have a look, akakak.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Shugo_002_Idle_S
string.body: Do you want to have a look at the Shugo specialties?

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1NPC_001_Idle_S
string.body: The Kerubs have been particularly persistent lately.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1NPC_002_Idle_S
string.body: We really are in big trouble, with all our crops plundered.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Guard_003_Idle_S
string.body: I believe even the Akarios village is in danger right now.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Guard_004_Idle_S
string.body: The Daminu forest is also quite eerie.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1NPC_004_Idle_S
string.body: Hey, keep quiet over there! All the fish are getting away!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Guard_005_Idle_S
string.body: The movements of the Kobolds have been quite suspicious.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Guard_006_Idle_S
string.body: Those darned Krall, just what do they have in mind, I wonder?

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1NPC_005_Idle_S
string.body: Ouch, my back! My whole body is aching.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1NPC_007_Idle_S
string.body: There is something ominous about the flow of Aether.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aGuard_001_Idle_S
string.body: The movements of Tursin of late have been...

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aGuard_002_Idle_S
string.body: Yet another large scale battle has begun in the Abyss.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aBroadCaster_001_Idle_B
string.body: Nesia has given birth to a son!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aBroadCaster_002_Idle_B
string.body: Please be careful! There are lots of things floating in the sky above the Citadel nowadays.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aBroadCaster_003_Idle_B
string.body: The general store is currently selling a selection of items at a low price.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aBroadCaster_004_Idle_B
string.body: The entrance of Tolbas Forest is infested with Worgs.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aBroadCaster_005_Idle_B
string.body: Uno from the Akarios village has won the 1st prize in the Sanctum Cooking Contest.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aBroadCaster_006_Idle_B
string.body: It is currently the Week of Pilgrimage. Please visit the Holy Ground and show your respect to the Five Empyrean Lords.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aBroadCaster_007_Idle_B
string.body: Gaurinerk and Toroonerk are providing consignment sales services. Please use it often, thank you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aBroadCaster_008_Idle_B
string.body: Poppy, a porgus from the Tolbas village, is gone missing. If you have seen Poppy then please contact Cannon.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aGuard_004_Idle_S
string.body: I guarantee the safety of the Tolbas village.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aNPC_001_Idle_S
string.body: I'm going crazy because of my worthless husband, really.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aNPC_002_Idle_S
string.body: Hurting the tree, the Wriggot is.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aNPC_003_Idle_S
string.body: A threat to the forest is also a threat to the Elim.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aNPC_004_Idle_S
string.body: I hear the song of trees.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aNPC_006_Idle_S
string.body: Must stop the Sapiens, to protect the forest.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aNPC_007_Idle_S
string.body: I sense the Aether is in its fullness.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aGuard_005_Idle_S
string.body: There is no anomaly in the flow of the Aether.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aGuard_006_Idle_S
string.body: Lepharist Revolutionaries are really getting on my nerves.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1_Mercenary_002_Atk_B
string.body: You've asked for it, I'll finish you all today!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1_Mercenary_003_Atk_B
string.body: These accursed wretches do not even tire!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_Mikero_1_idle_s
string.body: Just looking at you makes me want to recite a poem, [%username].

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_Mikero_2_idle_s
string.body: Oh, there is no one greater than [%username] under the skies of Atreia.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_Mikero_3_idle_s
string.body: All of Elysea shall come to their knees before [%username]'s name.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_Demodocos_1_idle_s
string.body: Hey, [%username]. Reading your face tells me that you will be wandering around for the rest of your life.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_Demodocos_2_idle_s
string.body: Beware when you board the ship, today. Your fortune says you'll fall overboard.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_Demodocos_3_idle_s
string.body: [%username], don't you have many concerns lately? Come and see me if you are curious about the future.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_Phokas_1_idle_s
string.body: The ship bound for the Outer Airship Dock will arrive soon!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_Phokas_2_idle_s
string.body: Please wait here for the ship if you want to go to the Outer Airship Dock!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_Phokas_3_idle_s
string.body: For your safety, please board the ship after it has completely stopped moving.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_Shugo_c19_1_idle_s
string.body: Careful when you board. You might fall if you aren't, akakak!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_Shugo_c19_2_idle_s
string.body: The ship is coming, the ship is coming, nyerk!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_Shugo_c19_3_idle_s
string.body: Make sure to visit Dionysia when you are in the Outer Airship Dock. The food there is fabulous, akakak.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Q2240_2_idle_B
string.body: It feels as if something might jump out.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Q2258_idle_B
string.body: Hmm, hmm, the young and exalted Archon Grak has subjugated Impetusium!

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1A_DF1_Jailer_1_idle_s
string.body: Be quiet! I'm telling you to keep your mouth shut.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1A_DF1_Jailer_2_idle_s
string.body: You lot are sadly mistaken if you thought Kinah would be useful here, you greedy pigs!

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1A_DF1_Jailer_3_idle_s
string.body: You dared to rebel against Lord Azphel! Even this dungeon is too good for the likes of you lot.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1A_DF1_Jailer_4_idle_s
string.body: Feh, you Balaur minion scums! You are all so dead.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1A_Irehilt_002_Atk_S
string.body: Ugh, they are trying to hurt me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1BroadCaster_001_Idle_B
string.body: Glory and praises to the protector of Atreia, the Empyrian Lady Ariel!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1BroadCaster_002_Idle_B
string.body: The Protectorate has achieved a tremendous victory in the Battle of Abyss!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1BroadCaster_003_Idle_B
string.body: The airship has arrived at the port! Please hurry if you are traveling to the Outer Port!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1BroadCaster_004_Idle_B
string.body: Verteron Citadel is currently recruiting Daevas who are willing to take part in removing the floating objects.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1BroadCaster_005_Idle_B
string.body: Please use the Hall of Prosperity if you wish to sell on consignment basis, thank you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1BroadCaster_006_Idle_B
string.body: Are you curious about your fortunes for today? Then please seek Demodocos in the Artisans Hall!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1BroadCaster_007_Idle_B
string.body: Heerunerk and Yiehmonerk are upgrading the Cubes at a bargain price in the Hall of Prosperity.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1BroadCaster_008_Idle_B
string.body: The Coliseum is waiting for Daevas who are willing to train their combat abilities. Please don't hesitate to visit the Coliseum if you are one of them.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF3_Little1_002_Idle_S
string.body: I'm afraid, of those filled with so much hate that they refuse to die even when they are dead.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF3_Little1_003_Idle_S
string.body: Save us from this hell, Lord Trajanus will

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF3_Little2_001_Idle_S
string.body: To fill the ends of my leaves, I want to drink the clear water.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF3_Little2_002_Idle_S
string.body: To fight against them, I am too weak.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF3_Little2_003_Idle_S
string.body: I fear more than death itself, turning into an Agrint.

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRoD2_003_Idle_S
string.body: O Azphel! Please take a kindly interest in the Protector of Pandaemonium, [%username]!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRoD2_004_Idle_S
string.body: As [%username] has come, those Elyos packs are as good as dead!

string.name: STR_CHAT_GuardianAssassin_001_Atk_S
string.body: I'll not let you reach Lord Hellion!

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1a_Serpine_1_idle_s
string.body: Who the hell is it? Be gone if you're an Asmodian scum!

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1a_Serpine_2_idle_s
string.body: It is about time my Guardian comrades came to rescue me...

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1a_Serpine_3_idle_s
string.body: The food here is terrible, really. Even the porgus gruel would taste better than this.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1_Lycan_Captured_2_idle_s
string.body: Excuse me. Take me to see Captain Suthran, please.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1_Lycan_Captured_3_idle_s
string.body: We are emissaries from the Silver Mane tribe who came requesting for help. We aren't here to attack you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Araison_1_idle_s
string.body: Beholding thy majestic presence inspired me to come up with a wonderful poem, [%username].

string.name: STR_CHAT_Araison_2_idle_s
string.body: I, Araison, have composed a poem for thee, [%username]. Would thou like to hear it?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Araison_3_idle_s
string.body: Well well, I have yet another follower. I just can't help but being popular.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Epren_1_idle_s
string.body: Oh my! You saw, you saw that right? Master Araison looked at my direction and smiled at me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Epren_2_idle_s
string.body: We love you so much, Master Araison!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Epren_3_idle_s
string.body: That melancholy stare, razor-sharp nose, and the gentle voice... Aah, he is perfection itself!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Geiena_1_idle_s
string.body: Here, Master Araison! Geiena is here again today!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Geiena_3_idle_s
string.body: Sigh, I wonder what sort of woman Master Araison likes?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Agamo_1_idle_s
string.body: Ho-hum, I can't think of any musical motif today.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Agamo_2_idle_s
string.body: Should I compose a military march for the Archons on the battlefield?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Agamo_3_idle_s
string.body: It might be interesting to make music from the sound of flowing water.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Lindhog_1_idle_s
string.body: May the protection of Azphel be with [%username], who visited Pandaemonium!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Lindhog_2_idle_s
string.body: If you have come looking for a Class Master then please make your way to the Great Temple.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Lindhog_3_idle_s
string.body: Please use the Temple of Gold if you wish to sell on consignment basis, thank you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Lindhog_4_idle_s
string.body: This is an urgent message! Our Archon Legion has achieved a tremendous victory in the Battle of Abyss!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Lindhog_5_idle_s
string.body: Stores on the Prosperity Road have just been stocked with many new items.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Lindhog_6_idle_s
string.body: A teleport statue linking the Vifrost Bridge and Prosperity Road has been erected. Please use it often, thank you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Lindhog_7_idle_s
string.body: Mistress Deyla is looking for witnesses of the Temple of Artisans incident.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Eiren_1_idle_s
string.body: Hm, this shipment of fabrics looks pretty good. We may get some pretty good designs out of it.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Eiren_2_idle_s
string.body: How come they are still not here with the fabrics! I'll never deal with those scoundrels of the Quairerk Traders again.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Eiren_3_idle_s
string.body: Welcome, [%username]! Here to buy some new clothes? Lark will show you the clothes catalogue, so do browse carefully and make your decision.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Wise_1_idle_s
string.body: Huoh, the fire is a bit strong. I'd better reduce it.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Wise_2_idle_s
string.body: I wonder when will I become as good as Master Kinterun?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Veldina_1_idle_s
string.body: May there be blessing of prosperity on [%username]!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Veldina_3_idle_s
string.body: If you want to use the Legion warehouse, please enter the room behind me.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Emvelu_1_idle_s
string.body: [%username], how about going to the Apellbine Tavern since you haven't had supper yet? Its food is very cheap and delicious.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Emvelu_2_idle_s
string.body: A roasted Conide is a mere 150 Kinah at the Apellbine Tavern! Ah, it's just so cheap!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Emvelu_3_idle_s
string.body: Are you planning any social gathering? We Apellbine have exclusive rooms ready for such group customers.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Kanensa_1_idle_s
string.body: The air current feels rather precarious. I don't think the airship can leave the ground under these conditions.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Kanensa_2_idle_s
string.body: O the canyon-rushing wind, please stop your run for a little while.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Kanensa_3_idle_s
string.body: The wind has stopped! Please board the airship quickly, hurry.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Annju_1_idle_s
string.body: It's OK. Nobody would have seen it...

string.name: STR_CHAT_Annju_2_idle_s
string.body: Oh, should I flee from here? If a Shadow Executor caught me while I stayed here...

string.name: STR_CHAT_Annju_3_idle_s
string.body: Calm down, Annju! You did nothing wrong! All you did was buying a ticket for someone!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Skia_1_idle_s
string.body: What would happen to the value of Daevas and Humans if we were to return to the flow of Aether?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Skia_2_idle_s
string.body: Is Aether really equal for everybody? Does that mean Daevas and Humans are also equal, too?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Skia_3_idle_s
string.body: Are the Aether that comprise our body and the Aether that we consume to exert power identical, or are they something totally different altogether?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Bodrug_1_idle_s
string.body: That would depend on where you place the value itself, wouldn't it?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Bodrug_2_idle_s
string.body: I think the concept of what Aether is must be established first before we could discuss that particular subject.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Bodrug_3_idle_s
string.body: Hm... Don't you think it would be best to ask that question to Master Sterlin?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Herpa_1_idle_s
string.body: Aren't you thirsty, [%username]? The Ringa juice of our Apellbine is perfect for quenching thirst, you know!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Herpa_2_idle_s
string.body: You hardly visit us these days, [%username]! At this rate I'll even forget what you look like.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Herpa_3_idle_s
string.body: Welcome, [%username]! Please go inside and taste the Mosbear honey cookies we just baked.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1aBroadCaster_001_Idle_B
string.body: Lepharist Revolutionaries have shown up at the Altgard Ice Lake. Please take extra care when you visit the lake.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1aBroadCaster_002_Idle_B
string.body: They are looking for workers in Impetusium. Please inquire to Banatisai if you are interested.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1aBroadCaster_003_Idle_B
string.body: The Moslan Forest is shrouded in a thick fog. Please be ware of Karnifs if you are going to the forest.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1aBroadCaster_004_Idle_B
string.body: Mosbears are running wild near the Basfelt Village. Common villagers should refrain from visiting the Basfelt Village, for now.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1aBroadCaster_005_Idle_B
string.body: Anyone who has seen Sapiens or the Lepharist Revolutionaries near the fortress should report it to an Archon Sentinel at once.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1aBroadCaster_006_Idle_B
string.body: Leinolz the herder has gone missing. If anyone knows where he is, then please contact his fianc Irehilt.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Monster_FakeGrailKeeper_Q2036_001_Atk_S
string.body: Foolish one, you shall pay dearly for this!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Monster_FakeGrailKeeper_Q2036_002_Atk_S
string.body: Death is the price you will pay for your greed!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF2BroadCaster_001_Idle_B
string.body: Asmodians have been infiltrating through a Rift. All residents should be on their guard.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF2BroadCaster_002_Idle_B
string.body: There have been an increasing number of robberies by Manduris lately. Please be careful when you are going through the Manduri Forest.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF2BroadCaster_003_Idle_B
string.body: The desertification of Eltnen is becoming more serious. Please put your efforts into protecting the Mystic Spring and trees.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF2BroadCaster_004_Idle_B
string.body: A strange creature is being seen every night in the Kuriullu Mountain. Please be careful when you are visiting the Agairon Village.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF2BroadCaster_005_Idle_B
string.body: You cannot use the Mystic Spring of Laquepin at the moment because a small problem has occurred.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF2BroadCaster_006_Idle_B
string.body: Eracus Temple Cavern is a dangerous place. Please bear in mind that common villagers are forbidden to go near the place.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF2BroadCaster_001_Idle_B
string.body: Elyos have been infiltrating through a Rift. All residents should be on their guard.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF2BroadCaster_002_Idle_B
string.body: If you have any clue about the Daeva who has gone missing lately, then please contact the Centurion or Anund.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF2BroadCaster_003_Idle_B
string.body: If you want to receive a Coin Quest or a reward, then please go and visit Coin Administrator Nott or Vebna.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF2BroadCaster_004_Idle_B
string.body: Taygas have been raiding the fortress at night. Please be careful when you are out during the night.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF2BroadCaster_005_Idle_B
string.body: Use of the Halabana Hot Springs is now prohibited. Let there be no unfortunate accidents by approaching the hot spring, please.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF2BroadCaster_006_Idle_B
string.body: A protection order has been issued for the Elim in the Patamor Thicket. We hope for much interest and cooperation from the residents.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Ab1BroadCasterL_001_Idle_B
string.body: The battle mothership of the Balaur, Dredgion, has been seen often lately. Please be extra careful when you move to another region.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Ab1BroadCasterL_002_Idle_B
string.body: The battles for the artifact continue to rage in the Sulfur Archipelago.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Ab1BroadCasterL_003_Idle_B
string.body: Asmodians are continuing their provocations in the upper Western Shard of Latesran. Please be on your guard, and do not fall for their evil lies.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Ab1BroadCasterL_004_Idle_B
string.body: The number of Balaur are increasing on the Drakenwreck. All Daevas must rise up to drive the Balaur out. For the glory of Sanctum!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Ab1BroadCasterL_005_Idle_B
string.body: More and more Daevas are disappearing near the Solitary Island. As we don't know what is happening yet, please be careful when you pass near the area.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF2BroadCasterD_001_Idle_B
string.body: The battle mothership of the Balaur, Dredgion, has been seen often lately. Please be extra careful when you move to another region.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF2BroadCasterD_002_Idle_B
string.body: The battles for the artifact continue to rage in the Sulfur Archipelago.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF2BroadCasterD_003_Idle_B
string.body: Elyos are continuing their provocations in the upper Eastern Shard of Latesran. Please be on your guard, and do not be tricked for their wicked schemes.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF2BroadCasterD_004_Idle_B
string.body: The number of Balaur are increasing at the Grave of Claws. It is time for all Daevas to rise up to drive the Balaur out. For the prosperity of Pandaemonium!

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF2BroadCasterD_005_Idle_B
string.body: More and more Daevas are disappearing near the Shade Island. As we don't know what is happening yet, please be careful when you pass near the area.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDF3_lp_Stein_001_Idle_s
string.body: I'm... Thirsty. If only I could have a sip of wine.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDF3_lp_Stein_002_Idle_s
string.body: Just one cup of Kirka Wine will stop this pain...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDF3_lp_Stein_003_Idle_s
string.body: Wine... Give me wine. Just a sip of Kirka wine...

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF2a_Guardian_001_Idle_B
string.body: Wait, [%username]! Are you really heading for the Parched Barrens? That area is very dangerous.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF2a_Guardian_002_Idle_B
string.body: Where are you going? The Parched Barrens is really dangerous. You must be very careful.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF2a_ArchonGuard_001_Idle_B
string.body: Wait, [%username]! Are you really heading for Sudorville? That area is very dangerous.

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF2a_ArchonGuard_002_Idle_B
string.body: Where are you going? If you are heading for Sudorville, you must be very careful.

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_034_Batk_S
string.body: Aren't you reckless, to come alone to face me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_035_Atk_S
string.body: Haha, not bad, not bad at all! But this might be too much for you to handle!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAB1_Dreadgion_ShugoExhausted_002_Idle_S
string.body: I must escape...Escape from here, nyerk.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTemple_Fanatic_001_Idle_S
string.body: You brute! Why harm Lord Vallakhan?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTemple_Fanatic_002_Idle_S
string.body: Help! Lord Vallakhan is in danger!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTemple_Fanatic_003_Idle_S
string.body: By Fregion's might! How could this happen?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Palentine_002_Idle_S
string.body: Here, try these. They're from a new line.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Mione_001_Idle_S
string.body: What are you are wearing, [%username]? Carrin can make you something much better.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Mione_002_Idle_S
string.body: Old man Daskin is going down!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Timogand_002_Idle_S
string.body: Really? You think that [%mainslotitem] matches your outfit? Pull the other one.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Horitius_01_001_Idle_S
string.body: Inggison Outpost is looking for skilled [%userclass]%.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Horitius_01_002_Idle_S
string.body: For your own safety, passengers heading for Soteria Sanctuary should board the Aethercraft.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Horitius_01_003_Idle_S
string.body: Sanctum flight 714 will be leaving from the Aerolink. Please form an orderly line at the east end of the square.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Horitius_02_001_Idle_S
string.body: It's awful! The Altar of Avarice and the Temple of Scales have fallen to the Asmodians.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Horitius_02_002_Idle_S
string.body: All Elyos in Inggison! Please, hurry to defend Inggison Outpost!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Horitius_02_003_Idle_S
string.body: We must help Veille the Agent. Let's all try the Blessing of Concentration!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Etard_01_001_Idle_S
string.body: Someone just told me a Dredgion has crashed on the Antagor Battlefield!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Etard_01_002_Idle_S
string.body: For your own safety, travelers heading for Rhonnam Refugee Village should board the Aethercraft.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Etard_02_001_Idle_S
string.body: Shards! The Glow-worms have taken the Vorgaltem Citadel and the Crimson Temple.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Etard_02_002_Idle_S
string.body: Asmodians in Gelkmaros! Gelkmaros Defense Base needs your strength! Now!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Etard_02_003_Idle_S
string.body: Azphel's shadow falls on Mastarius the Agent. Give him your strongest Blessing of Devotion!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Wonded_01_Idle_S
string.body: Just a flesh wound, nothing more...

string.name: STR_CHAT_Wonded_02_Idle_S
string.body: Hello? Doctor? Any doctor? There are healers in this place, right?

string.name: STR_CHAT_SWonded_02_Idle_S
string.body: Argh, I can't lay here like this...

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF4_Guard_02_Idle_S
string.body: No one will stand in our way.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF4_Guard_01_Atk_S
string.body: Prepare to die for what you've done.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF4_ShugoSupplyer_01_Idle_S
string.body: I move boxes here. I move boxes there. Then move boxes back. Sometimes I think, just leave boxes where they are.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF4_ShugoMaker_01_Idle_S
string.body: Ah, so good to see you! Let me squeeze you into my schedule.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDElim_Enalethe_Wounded
string.body: Are you just going to stand there and watch? Please come and help!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDElim_Enalethe_Die
string.body: Ouch, to be done in by some bugs...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDElim_Enalethe_Win
string.body: Thank you, [%userclass]. You really saved me there.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDElim_Hyas_Idle
string.body: Damn! I'm always out of breath whenever I get to Taloc. Gasp... Gasp...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDElim_Hyas_Despawn
string.body: Gasp...Gasp, I can't stand it anymore! I'm sorry but I'll leave first.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_ShulackWorker_01_Idle_s
string.body: How much longer do I have to carry this around? I want to go home!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDreadgion_02_ShulackWorker_02_Idle_s
string.body: Leave? Leave! And run into a Balaur guard? No sharding way.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDElim_Engeius_Yell_02
string.body: I am a Templar. I will protect you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDElim_Abyla_Yell_02
string.body: I am a Cleric. I can cast healing magic.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDElim_Engeius_Yell_03
string.body: Will you accompany me? Tell me if you will.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDElim_Abyla_Yell_03
string.body: Let me know if you need my help.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDElementalGossip44_02_Idle_S
string.body: Tuali served Davlin... But something's wrong with him now...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDElementalGossip55_01_Idle_S
string.body: Do you hear those noises coming from the rock?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDElementalGossip66_01_Idle_S
string.body: There are too many Macori! Kutol is scary...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDElementalGossip66_02_Idle_S
string.body: They have a leader... It's Kutol, Kutol...

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF4_IDArenaGossip_02_Idle
